PrecisRegulations Amending the HEALTH OF ANIMALS REGULATIONS by establishing a National Cattle Identification Program whereby every bovine animal must be identified with an official tag before leaving its herd of origin or before mingling with the cattle of other producers, effective January 1, 2001.
